{"tid":52383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2016-12-24T04:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T23:41:48.000Z","uid":14478,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90d8e76d5e3d13e5ecad3ccff0dde9136768c8da","tid":52383,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"16cca65ebb60f2a795122eda5a11f89a0880b9f0","tid":52383,"uid":63187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"link"},{"pid":"63e77ddeaa9b3aa90079cc7134e838fbb5f6d1ab","tid":52383,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"咁抵比人唱啦"},{"pid":"120cf07752fb3b5e016764347c22ade0671f8d3e","tid":52383,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"明明係自己柒，仲好意思嬲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f9ac105e1b6802fd5e8f9abe02c9b39afdf976","tid":52383,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8985948f3dd126707cb79e8cd6aac7092c14e2ab","tid":52383,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"今年竟然冇人post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMerry Christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007f96214f05906162362dcff5ebfa1383a63add","tid":52383,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:40